cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.HC, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on human-robot interaction and manipulation, which is a core topic in robotics (cs.RO). The use of annotations and object modeling also involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) techniques. The goal of reducing the complexity of CAD-like interfaces suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the use of machine learning and AI techniques may also be relevant (cs.AI).
